Package com.camerontec.catalys.server.sessionmanager

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IClientConnectionManager
    Interface for objects which establish a party connection and log on to a session.
    ISessionManager
    An object that controls the FIX Session for a given ConnectionPoint.
    ISessionManagerListener
    Listeners to SessionManager's should implement this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnonymousPartyIdentifier
    Session customizer implementation which knows how to validate a party, implied by a FIX message, based on the server's configuration.
    ApplicationLogonConnectionManager  
    CIDRNotationChecker
    CIDR: Classless Inter-Domain Routing
    DefaultClientConnectionManager
    This object establishes a party connection and logs on a session.
    MessageCountsStatsService
    This service keep track of the number of FIX messages processed by each FIX session throughout the day regardless of sequence number resets.
    ServerConnectionManager
    Listens for connections on given port.
    SessionCommandLineProcessor
    This is the command line interface for Sessions.
    SessionManager
    Standard implementation of ISessionManager.
    SessionStatusListenerBase
    Base implementation of ISessionStatusListener.
    UserPassFromPasswordStoreClientConnectionManager
    Specialised client connection manager uses the configured IPasswordStoreWithMemory to obtain a password for the configured username and send those in Logon message in Username(tag #553) and Password(tag #554).
